{"tid":274162,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭屋企擺 Server 有著數，沖涼熱水唔使錢","createTime":"2017-06-07T06:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T03:46:53.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39ae056f6c69680ee7fcbe07301cb4dcce81aec6","tid":274162,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"使用電腦會發出熱力，而伺服器亦一樣；數據中心內有數以萬計的伺服器，產生的熱力可想而知，要解決散熱問題，就要花費金錢和耗費能源。為了降低散熱的開支，有數據中心設置在北極圈附近，又嘗試將伺服器搬至深海。荷蘭一間初創公司 Nerdalize 則採取另類途徑，嘗試將熱力好好利用。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/06/03/free-hot-shower-using-heat-from-server/life-tech/green-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2Ffree-hot-shower-using-heat-from-server%2Flife-tech%2Fgreen-2%2F&d=RqhwnB06MJQCJkBLgkiVqjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3bc4bb99\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/06/03/free-hot-shower-using-heat-from-server/life-tech/green-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/142258_f2efb246e973426080c9819c9cfcb539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F142258_f2efb246e973426080c9819c9cfcb539.jpg&h=5dfda9fb&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nNerdalize 的方案好簡單，用戶向 Nerdalize 支付安裝伺服器的費用，伺服器就會取代暖氣系統為用戶的家居提供熱能。Nerdalize 在 2015 年發表第一款擁有發熱能力的伺服器產品，不過當時效能緩慢，要接近 1 小時才能發熱，而且熱力只足以溫暖小房間，現時 Nerdalize 終於推出第二代的產品。<br />\n<br />\n今年 8 月開始，Nerdalize 會在荷蘭為 42 個家庭安裝第二代伺服器，主力為家居提供熱水。Nerdalize 表示家庭安裝他們的伺服器，可以每年節省約 300 歐元的燃料費用，至於租用伺服器的商戶則可以節省約 50% 的使費。此外 Nerdalize 的伺服器還可以減少家庭的碳排放約 3 公噸，是一個三贏的方案。Nerdalize 正透過眾籌平台募集資金進一步開發，但首先要解決資料保安的問題，如何說服客戶將資料存放在一般家庭而非數據中心。<br />\n<br />\n來源：theverge"},{"pid":"44e792589df4d529579968fe4eaa0d3a45d31cd9","tid":274162,"uid":67527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"點解決bandwidth問題，咪玩啦"},{"pid":"89184abed8e59eec0884a6807d2a4be9fece1ba5","tid":274162,"uid":3595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:18:14.000Z","msg":"如果嗰家人玩野或者去旅行熄左總制<br />\n咁部野係咪都會熄埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5483249f8a9ec546cc05cbbe6fe96c1d29730c","tid":274162,"uid":47823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"將核電廠放入屋企 餘熱用不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b69b94ef84e108cc10632d3e2418b06999d90d7","tid":274162,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:33:48.000Z","msg":"夏天點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bb4728b191b74d9d83b4faa3b2861615f9beb9","tid":274162,"uid":3595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夏天點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢嗰啲地方應該長年都係凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3f12cd1f26d07e58d375c6f6f76355a94da442","tid":274162,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>夏天點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢嗰啲地方應該長年都係凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個次係AMS<br />\n明明係北半球既六月<br />\n但氣溫得十零度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b2e5d9615e279d15b81ab7c7837ab3ac9ea5db","tid":274162,"uid":839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>夏天點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢嗰啲地方應該長年都係凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個次係AMS<br />\n明明係北半球既六月<br />\n但氣溫得十零度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尋日凍到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e2d48e880efefcc75901d932973cdea1f53bad","tid":274162,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T23:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解決bandwidth問題，咪玩啦</blockquote><br />\n緊係會自己再駁線啦<br />\n唔通搶你屋企上網咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15937d431ad2cdc982fcf18d25f9b40fd08891cd","tid":274162,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解決bandwidth問題，咪玩啦</blockquote><br />\n緊係會自己再駁線啦<br />\n唔通搶你屋企上網咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果可以用到server 嘅10% bandwidth 咁我諗個個都狗衝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2719506bc163654425ecd63f3d3f39c83664e6","tid":274162,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解決bandwidth問題，咪玩啦</blockquote><br />\n緊係會自己再駁線啦<br />\n唔通搶你屋企上網咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每一戶駁條光纖比你係好貴(外國唔流行架)，而且數據中心好多嘢都係distributed computing，搞遠距離networking係好難，個latency可以好難控制"}]}